oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Gay Street
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Thompson Brothers
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Gay Street looking south, Knoxville, TN. Partial view of __L. Stephenson Co., Woodruff's Hardware at left. Miller's, movie theatre, Anderson Dulin Varnell sign, and partial view of Kress at right. Cars, wagons and bicycles in street, people on sidewalk. Ca. 1920.
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Streets; Business enterprises; Automobiles; Carts & wagons;
